{"tid":1751753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[冷水]其實以選票數量嚟講，只可以講話小勝","createTime":"2019-11-24T18:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T18:17:23.000Z","uid":87507,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3f88efab1ef2472916d8cef423de58713b84f358","tid":1751753,"uid":87507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:03:04.000Z","msg":"依家以票數嚟講都係講，都係多一兩成，證明藍絲仲係為數不少。<br />\n<br />\n而且區議會唔係終點，請不要驕傲，我哋仲有大把野要做"},{"pid":"fc7ecf655c7b1aee103f6f839e6b900ca46d143b","tid":1751753,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:03:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咪撚做休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投完票，贏輸都好，我地有新野做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣方向：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 有得一人一票，社會氣氛好左幾多？而且大家都相信投票，年青人到長者教出黎投，所以應該一人一票選特首。<br />\n<br />\n2.我地要將種票、票多過投票人、送禮各種唔公平現象比英美兩國知。<br />\n<br />\n3. Poly手足被困多日，要求警察撤退。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water be humble </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5cf2b762f3366090e500f7511dc73ae9de443c4e","tid":1751753,"uid":42734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:03:49.000Z","msg":"所以立法會唔會大勝"},{"pid":"0354d231e2123a3d49454b039dbdb27f235b2e81","tid":1751753,"uid":159166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:04:16.000Z","msg":"當中有好多都係老人院同埋大陸人"},{"pid":"06dc600388916648b80866c3dfe20d4c5a54fcb2","tid":1751753,"uid":87507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0354d231e2123a3d49454b039dbdb27f235b2e81","tid":1751753,"uid":159166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy